# PrivOTC CRE Environment Variables

# ============================================
# MetaMask Wallet Configuration (REQUIRED)
# ============================================
# Your MetaMask wallet private key for:
# 1. Deploying CRE workflow
# 2. Executing on-chain settlements
# 3. Paying gas fees
#
# How to get:
# 1. Open MetaMask
# 2. Three dots (⋮) → Account Details
# 3. Export Private Key
# 4. Enter password → Copy key
#
# ⚠️ SECURITY WARNING:
# - NEVER commit this file to GitHub
# - NEVER share your private key
# - Use a dedicated wallet (not your main wallet)
# - Ensure wallet has Sepolia ETH for gas fees
#
CRE_ETH_PRIVATE_KEY=0xYOUR_METAMASK_PRIVATE_KEY_HERE

# ============================================
# World ID Configuration (Already Set in Config)
# ============================================
# These are in privotc-config.json, not here:
# - worldIdAppId: app_staging_356707253a6f729610327063d51fe46e
# - worldIdAction: submit_trade
#
# World ID is for END USERS (not for CRE deployment)
#
# DO NOT add World ID credentials here!

# ============================================
# Optional: Custom RPC Endpoints
# ============================================
# If you want to override RPC URLs in project.yaml
# SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.infura.io/v3/YOUR_KEY
# TENDERLY_FORK_URL=https://rpc.tenderly.co/fork/YOUR_FORK_ID

# ============================================
# Deployment Checklist
# ============================================
# Before deploying:
# 1. ✅ Get contract addresses from Dev 1
# 2. ✅ Update privotc-config.production.json
# 3. ✅ Add your MetaMask private key above
# 4. ✅ Fund wallet with 0.1 Sepolia ETH
# 5. ✅ Apply for CRE Early Access
# 6. ✅ Test: cre workflow simulate
# 7. ✅ Deploy: cre workflow deploy
